e px-4 py-2">Field Deployments</span> <span class="rounded-full text-slate-700 border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2">Special Situations</span></div></div></section><section class="relative mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl z-10 pb-16"><div class="space-y-10"><article class="border bg-white border-gray-200 group overflow-hidden p-6 relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl sm:p-8"><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 relative"><div class="md:w-2/5"><div class="border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl"><img alt="Itinerant polymath who shows up and solves problems visual" class="transition aspect-square duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.03] object-cover w-full" src="/static/angel.jpg" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="flex-1"><div class="flex flex-wrap font-semibold gap-3 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase"><span class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary">DFS</span> <span class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-700 bg-slate-100">Special Contract / Integration</span> <span class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700">Remote-friendly</span></div><h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mt-4 text-2xl"><a class="transition hover:text-primary" href="/jobs/itinerant-polymath">Itinerant polymath who shows up and solves problems</a></h2><p class="text-slate-600 mt-1 text-lg">Drop in, enlight us, and disseapear</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 text-slate-500 text-sm"><span class="items-center inline-flex gap-1"><span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-500 h-2 w-2"></span> Earth and beyond / Remote </span><span>Posted Nov 21, 2025</span></div><p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600">We occasionally need someone who can show up, absorb context fast, and fix the unsolvable.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6"><span class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-700 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase">special-projects </span><span class="rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-700 bg-slate-50 border bo